  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3329370/" class="title-link">文字、义理、书法三者具精</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3329370"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4155860/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4155860-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4155860/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">xfisher</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-13"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-13 12:52:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3329370_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  文字、义理、书法三者具精。中国经典之书，有经典之注（四书、周易均为朱子注），犹贵在四书字体之书法（如其字、意，浩然中正）。惜为缩印本，字太小，读注字犹其费力。但此书实为经典版本。

